HEADWORD: Austerlitz
<hw>Austerlitz</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a decisive battle during the
Napoleonic campaigns (1805); the French under Napoleon defeated the
Russian and Austrian armies of Czar Alexander I and Emperor Francis
II.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> battle of Austerlitz.</syn>⟦br⟧
